Why Choose GoRide?

Compliance and safety

Certified by the Japan Transport Bureau. premium vehicles driven by licensed and insured professionals.

Easy booking&order　management

Easy one-page booking, with instant confirmation and flexible online changes & cancellations.

Sustainability

We proudly offer an array of electric vehicles and ensure our carbon footprint is offset!

Transparent pricing

One clear rate with no hidden fees—tolls, parking, and surcharges are all covered.

Plenty of Fleet

From luxury minivans to EVs and microbuses, our diverse lineup ensures comfort, safety, and style for every occasion.

Multilingual Service

Our  support team provides multilingual assistance,ensuring seamless communication and peace of mind throughout your journey.
